---
import BlogPostLayout from "../../layouts/BlogPostLayout.astro";
import BlogByline from "../../components/BlogByline.astro";
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";

// Make this page dynamic via SSR
export const prerender = false;

const publishDate = new Date("May 25 2026");
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

---

<BlogPostLayout
  title="Move-Out Cleaning Costs Nashville 2026"
  schemaTitle="Move-Out Cleaning Costs in Nashville: 2026 Updated Guide"
  description={isPublished ? "Move-out cleaning costs in Nashville for 2026: real pricing by neighborhood, what's included, and how to protect your security deposit. Updated guide for tenants." : "Coming Soon: Move-Out Cleaning Costs in Nashville: 2026 Updated Guide"}
  publishDate={publishDate}
  noindex={!isPublished}
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Pricing/Direct Response
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Move-Out Cleaning Costs in Nashville: 2026 Updated Guide
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming May 25 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="mb-8">
          <BlogByline variant="dark" date={publishDate} readTime={readTime} />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <!-- DIRECT ANSWER BLOCK - Critical for AEO -->
        <div
          class="bg-[#FFA985]/10 border-l-4 border-[#FFA985] p-6 mb-8 rounded-r-lg"
        >
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-medium mb-0">
            <strong>Quick Answer:</strong> Move-out cleaning in Nashville costs
            between $200 and $500 in 2026 for most homes. The final price depends
            on the size of the property, how much cleaning is needed, and any
            add-ons like carpet shampooing or interior appliance cleaning. A
            thorough, checklist-driven clean is the single best way to protect
            your security deposit.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          How Much Does Move-Out Cleaning Cost in Nashville in 2026?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          The cost of move-out cleaning in Nashville for 2026 varies depending on
          several factors, with average prices ranging from <strong>$200 to
          $500</strong>. The final cost depends on the size of the property, the
          level of cleaning required, and your specific service needs.
          Understanding these elements helps you budget effectively and ensures
          your space is ready for its next chapter.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          What Factors Affect Move-Out Cleaning Costs?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Several key factors influence the pricing of move-out cleaning services
          in Nashville. Here's what to consider:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
          <li>
            <strong>Size of the property:</strong> Larger homes require more time
            and resources, which increases the cost.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Level of cleaning required:</strong> Standard cleaning is less
            expensive than a
            <a href="/services/deep-cleaning" class="text-[#FFA985] hover:underline"
              >deep clean</a
            >, which may be necessary if the property hasn't been maintained
            regularly.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Additional services:</strong> Extras like carpet shampooing,
            window washing, and interior appliance cleaning add to the total.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          What to Expect During a Move-Out Cleaning
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Here's a breakdown of what a professional move-out cleaning typically
          includes:
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Kitchen</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-0">
              Deep cleaning of all surfaces, inside-and-out appliance cleaning,
              and floor scrubbing.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Bathrooms</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-0">
              Thorough cleaning of tiles, toilets, sinks, and mirrors to remove
              every trace of use.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
              Living Areas &amp; Bedrooms
            </h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-0">
              Dusting, vacuuming, and mopping to leave each room spotless.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Additional Areas</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-0">
              Basements, garages, and outdoor spaces can be included on request.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          Why Choose The Valley Clean Team for Your Move-Out Clean?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Choosing The Valley Clean Team means choosing reliability, precision,
          and meticulous attention to detail. Our veteran-owned team brings
          military-grade accountability to every job.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
          <li>
            <strong>Guaranteed satisfaction:</strong> We follow a 49-point
            checklist with post-clean photos so nothing gets missed.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Transparent pricing:</strong> The price you see is the price
            you pay—no surprise charges.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Community focused:</strong> As a local team serving Nashville,
            we understand what landlords and property managers expect.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          How to Compare Move-Out Cleaning Services
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          When selecting a move-out cleaning service, weigh these criteria:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
          <li>
            <strong>Reputation:</strong> Look for reviews and testimonials that
            speak to reliability and results.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Experience:</strong> A team with a proven move-out track
            record delivers a deposit-ready clean.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Flexibility:</strong> Choose a service that can accommodate
            your moving schedule and any special requests.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
          How to Book Your Move-Out Cleaning
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Booking with The Valley Clean Team is straightforward and stress-free:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600 list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
          <li>
            <strong>Get a free quote:</strong> Tell us about your property for an
            upfront estimate based on your specific needs.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Schedule your service:</strong> Pick a convenient time for our
            specialists to perform the clean.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Relax and reclaim your time:</strong> Focus on your move while
            we handle the cleaning.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <!-- CLOSING CTA -->
        <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-xl text-center mt-12">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Reclaim Your Time—Book Today
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
            Don't let the stress of moving weigh you down. Get a free quote in
            under 2 hours. No obligation.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a
              href="tel:6155101427"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition"
            >
              <Icon name="phone" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />Call 615-510-1427
            </a>
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white border-2 border-white rounded-full hover:bg-white/10 transition"
            >
              Request Quote Online
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">May 25 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )}
  <!-- Nashville Services CTA -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-[#FFA985]/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Move-Out Cleaning Services in Nashville, TN
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
        The Valley Clean Team helps Nashville renters and landlords get deposits back
        with thorough, checklist-driven move-out cleans.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="/locations/nashville"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-[#FFA985] text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition"
        >
          View Nashville Services
        </a>
        <a
          href="/locations/nashville/move-out-cleaning/"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-[#FFA985] text-[#FFA985] font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-[#FFA985] hover:text-white transition"
        >
          Get a Move-Out Quote
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BlogPostLayout>
